# CoCo Platform — Local Configuration Template

## What This Is
Copy this file to `CLAUDE.local.md` and customize for your environment.
CLAUDE.local.md is gitignored and will not be committed.

## Your Configuration
- **Working directory:** /path/to/coco-platform
- **Backend:** Python 3.13 + FastAPI + uvicorn
- **Frontend:** React 19 + Vite 6 + Radix UI + Tailwind CSS 4
- **Package managers:** uv (backend), pnpm (frontend)

## Your Data Stores
- `~/.hub/hub.db` — Knowledge Hub (read-only)
- `~/.coco/platform.db` — Platform database (read-write)
- `~/.coco/brain.json` — People graph and rules
- `~/.coco/config.json` — CoCo configuration

## Conventions
- Backend tests: `pytest`
- Frontend tests: `vitest`
- Commit format: `{sprint}.{task}: {description}`
